{"tid":1756214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"願榮光歸香港出左意大利文版!","createTime":"2019-11-26T02:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T02:45:56.000Z","uid":326280,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8b154f366a6e26f5c75706a6d95cbe40850734","tid":1756214,"uid":326280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"由意大利男高音手足Stefano Lodola演唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-Cl09If1XbE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-Cl09If1XbE&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV03GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=d39a6fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-Cl09If1XbE</a><br />\n<br />\n其實呢位意大利巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14年雨革個陣來過香港唱do you hear the people sing<br />\n佢今年九月尾已經系香港 所有野自費 一豪子都無收過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7HiGNp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7HiGNp.png&h=9e9428d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩個月以來好似都系住重慶大廈d hostel 最平個d十幾人房 佢本身生得高 張床對佢來講太細 訓覺都唔可以伸直個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢唔單止擅長唱歌 講個秘密你聽<br />\n佢其實系國際高智商組織Mensa既會員來<br />\n識好多國語言 最近仲學緊廣東話<br />\n之前唔識廣東話 為左唱廣東話版既願榮光歸香港 <br />\n好努力甘逐個字逐個字學發音<br />\n<br />\np.s. 其實宜家總共有幾多語言版本？<br />\n我所知有<br />\n廣東話<br />\n台語<br />\n普通話/國語<br />\n英文<br />\n日文<br />\n韓文<br />\n德文<br />\n意大利文<br />\n仲有呢？"},{"pid":"b166f18252a26e7c3f5772275442f4743d706f78","tid":1756214,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線勿鬆懈！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" dat